<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<key>aps-environment</key>
	<string>production</string>
	<!-- Tap to Pay on iPhone — Apple GRANTED the request 2026-07-02 (Case-ID 20814883,
	     dev-distribution tier), BUT as of 2026-07-02 the entitlement had NOT yet propagated
	     to the com.gotvero.app App ID: automatic signing failed with "entitlement ...
	     proximity-reader.payment.acceptance not found and could not be included in profile,"
	     and "Tap to Pay on iPhone" did not appear under Xcode's + Capability. Temporarily
	     removed again so the app builds. RE-ADD once the capability shows up under
	     Signing & Capabilities → + Capability → "Tap to Pay on iPhone" (add it THAT way so
	     Xcode registers it with the App ID, not by hand-editing this file). -->
</dict>
</plist>
